| x_1 + x_2 + ... + x_n  | \leq | x_1 | + | x_2| + \ldots + | x_n |
|a+b| \leq |a| + |b|
n=k
n = k+1
 \text{Let n = 2 } \\ \implies LHS = | 1 + 2 | = |3| = 3 \\ \implies RHS = | 1 | + | 2| = 1 + 2 = 3 \\ \text{Therefore I have proved it for n = 2 } \\ \text{Assume that $n=k$ is true, Let $n = k+1$} 
